<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #DC2626; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; }
        .alert { background: #FEE2E2; border-left: 4px solid #DC2626; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #DC2626; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; padding: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{ user.email }},</p>
            
            <div class="alert">
                <strong>Action Required:</strong> We were unable to process your payment for {{ team.name }}.
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{ payment.failureReason ?? 'Payment declined' }}</p>
            
            <p><strong>Plan:</strong> {{ subscription.plan.name }} ({{ subscription.plan.formattedPrice }})</p>
            
            {% if retry_count < 3 %}
            <p>We will automatically retry the payment in a few days. You can also update your payment method now to avoid any service interruption.</p>
            
            <p><strong>Retry Attempt:</strong> {{ retry_count }} of 3</p>
            {% else %}
            <p>We have attempted to charge your payment method 3 times without success. Your subscription will be suspended soon if payment is not received.</p>
            {% endif %}
            
            <a href="{{ url('payment_methods') }}" class="button">Update Payment Method</a>
            
            <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Your subscription remains active during the grace period</li>
                <li>We'll retry the payment automatically</li>
                <li>Update your payment method to avoid suspension</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} SaaS Starter Pack. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
